  "text": "We describe now the optimal control problem related to the Hamilton-Jacobi equation studied in [CITATION_1] [CITATION_2] . It is referred to as the regional control problem. The basic framework remains the same as for the FL framework, assumptions [H0]-[H1]-[H2] being exactlty the same. We keep the same notation when no difference arises between the two frameworks.",
